  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Eventually came back down again and see that the Germans gathered the corpses, and so on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And understood it is now under German control and never to come back.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Eventually [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] they decided that I cannot stay with them-- child among the group, in the middle of the winter, in the mountains of-- of Slovakia.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I went down from the mountain to a very, very small village called Buly, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] so small it's not on a map.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Again, what I told you before that I question my recollections, when I eventually got a map of Slovakia to try and retrace, there was no such place on the map.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There was another, bigger village-- the center, which is also a church, called Donovaly, and I found Donovaly on the map.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We actually have some artifacts from Donovaly, which I brought.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I couldn't find Buly, so I-- but again, Buly was there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Eventually, I found it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] He brought me to the edge of Buly and placed me with a family-- Christian family there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Now there are two versions of what happened when I was placed there-- his version and my recollection.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I have no reason to doubt his version, but maybe it's a bit more dramatized than it was, because my recollection doesn't agree with it totally.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Henry's version is that he brought me to the place and put me in the house of this family-- and I have the names.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I'll describe the house in a moment.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
